{"id":14318,"date":"2024-02-09T16:43:46","date_gmt":"2020-09-09T11:13:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=14318"},"modified":"2024-02-09T14:59:23","modified_gmt":"2024-02-09T09:29:23","slug":"four-poster-bed-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/four-poster-bed-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Four Poster Bed Design Ideas For Your Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>We have classic four-poster bed ideas here for you to read and enjoy.&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s get into a bit of history before we go mainstream. Four-poster beds were invented in the early 13th century and are now commonly known as canopy beds. Royal families used these beds in their castles. Back in the day instead of beams supporting curtains they supported fur to maintain privacy and also keep people warm when they were in bed. We all know castles back then were cold and not really like modern homes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Industrial Style Bedroom With Four-Poster Bed<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Industrial style of interior design has recently gained popularity because of its minimalistic yet rugged look. This bedroom is designed with brick-cladding walls and wooden flooring for a rustic yet comforting vibe. The four-poster bed in dark brown comes with grey cushioned upholstery and acts as the showstopper of this industrial bedroom. To add a pop of colour to the space, you can opt for a bright red accent chair like the one shown in the image. Add fairy lights or sheer curtains to decorate your four-poster bed for a dramatic effect.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120149\/four-poster-bed-in-industrial-style-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"A four poster bed in the industrial-style bedroom with string lights\" class=\"wp-image-42380\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120149\/four-poster-bed-in-industrial-style-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120149\/four-poster-bed-in-industrial-style-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120149\/four-poster-bed-in-industrial-style-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120149\/four-poster-bed-in-industrial-style-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sleek four-poster bed to match your industrial-style bedroom interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Customise your bed and enjoy up to 25 year warranty\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08210059\/customise-your-bed-enjoy-up-to-25-year-warranty.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beautiful Canopy Bed For Your Kids Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Canopy beds are an excellent addition to your kid&#8217;s room. They add a playful vibe and add dimension to your interiors. This four-poster canopy bed is designed with hidden storage where you can store your kid&#8217;s toys, bedsheets, pillow covers, etc. The blue and wood combination of this room creates a striking contrast and freshness to the entire space. Add some floor cushions and an anti-skid floor mat to add to the cosiness of the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120156\/four-poster-canopy-bed-for-kids.jpg\" alt=\"A four poster canopy bed in minimalist style for kids room\" class=\"wp-image-42381\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120156\/four-poster-canopy-bed-for-kids.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120156\/four-poster-canopy-bed-for-kids-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120156\/four-poster-canopy-bed-for-kids-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/11120156\/four-poster-canopy-bed-for-kids-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Modern four-poster bed design to add quirkiness to your kids room interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Floral Four-Poster Bed<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you love the idea of pretty flowers and enjoy the fresh aroma they emit, then this four-poster design is sure to blow your mind. The four-poster bed is decorated with fresh flowers on all four beams. Pretty flowers in white and pink with green leaves leave this four-poster bed looking gorgeous. White net curtains add to this floral drama giving it a touch of flowing beauty.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163333\/floral-four-poster-bed-curtains.jpg\" alt=\"A four poster bed curtains decorated with a fresh flower in the white bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-14321\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163333\/floral-four-poster-bed-curtains.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163333\/floral-four-poster-bed-curtains-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163333\/floral-four-poster-bed-curtains-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163333\/floral-four-poster-bed-curtains-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A four-poster bed with beams covered in flowers with a white net curtain<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Four Poster Paradise<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever imagined how heaven would look like? Well, let us make an attempt to leave you awestruck with this paradise on earth. This bedroom comes with walls, flooring and a four-poster bed all in white. We can safely say that the interior design of this space resembles heaven on earth with its angelic-style four-poster bed. The four-poster bed is decorated with elegant white curtains that stand tall when tied up. This bedroom has a Victorian touch to it with a console stool and antique headboard.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163226\/4-poster-bed-paradise-.jpg\" alt=\"A white four poster bed design in a victorian style in all-white bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-14320\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163226\/4-poster-bed-paradise-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163226\/4-poster-bed-paradise--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163226\/4-poster-bed-paradise--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163226\/4-poster-bed-paradise--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A victorian style bedroom with a four-poster bed and frosty white curtains<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Rustic Poster Bed Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This four-poster bed design is for kids or even teenagers as it has a single cot. This four-poster bed is made from wood and has white curtains to maintain the privacy that can be either tied up or let loose. The bed has a matching <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedside-table-designs\/\">bedside table<\/a> and a white cushioned pouffe.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163739\/rustic-poster-bed-design.jpg\" alt=\"A rustic four poster bed for India made from wood with white curtains\" class=\"wp-image-14325\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163739\/rustic-poster-bed-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163739\/rustic-poster-bed-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163739\/rustic-poster-bed-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163739\/rustic-poster-bed-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A blue accent wall bedroom with a four-poster bed made from wood with white curtains neatly pushed back to the headboard.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Modular, futuristic interiors for homes that priortise comfort!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/09144041\/modular-futuristic-interiors-for-homes-that-priortise-comfort.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Four Poster Decoration Idea With Rose Petals<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a big day coming up and need to pep up your bedroom? Check out this four-poster bed decoration idea. You will agree that your partner and you deserve nothing but the best. This king-sized four-poster bed with white sheets, matching curtains with rose petals scattered all over the bed and two elegant white swan towels is a perfect idea to make your special day more special for your loved one.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163535\/poster-bed-decoration-ideas-with-rose-petals-.jpg\" alt=\"A luxurious king-sized four-poster bed with crisp white sheets\" class=\"wp-image-14323\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163535\/poster-bed-decoration-ideas-with-rose-petals-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163535\/poster-bed-decoration-ideas-with-rose-petals--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163535\/poster-bed-decoration-ideas-with-rose-petals--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163535\/poster-bed-decoration-ideas-with-rose-petals--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A king-size four-poster bed decorated with towels made into swans and red rose petals<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pick A Pattern For Your Poster Bed Please<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are a pattern-on-pattern kind of person then these poster bed curtains are definitely for you. Take a look at this bedroom that has been designed with patterned wallpaper. See how it merges beautifully with the patterned curtains on this four-poster bed? A complete blue and white pattern on pattern theme is trippy yet somewhat satisfying if you love patterns.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163645\/poster-bed-design-with-patterned-walls.jpg\" alt=\"A four-poster bed design with matching curtains to a blue and white pattern bedroom wall\" class=\"wp-image-14324\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163645\/poster-bed-design-with-patterned-walls.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163645\/poster-bed-design-with-patterned-walls-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163645\/poster-bed-design-with-patterned-walls-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/09163645\/poster-bed-design-with-patterned-walls-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An English bedroom with patterned walls and matching curtains surrounded the beams of a four-poster bed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are a few questions we often get asked by our clients:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>1: Are four-poster beds out of style?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A: Four poster beds never go out of style. They are classics and have stayed that way for a long time now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>2: How do you dress a four-poster bed?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A: You can dress your four-poster bed by choosing your preferred choice of material for curtains. Make sure opulent fabric has been used as an overhead canopy and curtains at each corner for a true royal feel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>3: What is the top of a four-poster bed called?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A: It is usually called a rectangular panel that is made from the same material of the four-poster bed beams.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is what we at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> think are some amazing four-poster bed designs for your bedroom. We hope you enjoyed this read. Let us know what you think! Send us an email. Can&#8217;t wait to hear from you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You Can Also Check Out<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">Latest Bedroom Interior Designs By DesignCafe<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bed-designs\/\">Modern Bed Designs<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n